like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"建議以後考dse前考返個IQ test先 跟返IQ分數分組考 咁先最公平"},{"pid":"af7ac3d57787665b1b793f602b0935a42a2bdc5c","tid":2325864,"uid":55800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"907de7f8f37bcadc65aeac5dcf162392302c7686","tid":2325864,"uid":387165,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲會同支那人結婚嘅女人都唔慌係好野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔同支那人結婚，呢班女人賣港都係遲早嘅事<br />\n你要團結香港人，首先要鞏固香港人嘅民族意識，咁佢地自然就唔會亂咁同外族通婚"},{"pid":"d476745d70556af55341c6f9cf96f41ba2a5b3ba","tid":2325864,"uid":387165,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83eb70e10ea2af13f66ebd2ea2797c07628464a2","tid":2325864,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24027ef043becb70223481d81bb6080759347ab9","tid":2325864,"uid":125027,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"上個post已經睇清楚你只係想食住班男權撚上位做youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n某程度上同你反緊既女權撚kol一模一樣諗住靠兩性對立揾食<br />\n扑得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b86ad7f9e21b76ade1fdfdeb8988959a6c8a04e","tid":2325864,"uid":387165,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e30e3b05fe5506eeef68cbd14de8d89fb94da28","tid":2325864,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc6e8985ff42b00cc7ee7bf607ff48d66ade7b0c","tid":2325864,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女性發育比男性早<br />\n女性年輕領悟能力自然比男性強<br />\n呢個係定律，係基因定，唔係後天問題</blockquote>其實同中學收生方法有關<br />\n女仔發育就係小五小六<br />\n比起男仔去到中一二先開始<br />\n女仔入到好既學校就會比男仔高<br />\n所以以前係男女分隊就冇呢個問題<br />\n只不過近年取消左</blockquote>咁不如推遲個年紀，等埋你發左育先考試<br />\n推推下大家集體 25 歲先讀完大學畢業</blockquote><br />\n滑坡謬誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e182cb551a0579c784be4ed68b2a3af3b9f168","tid":2325864,"uid":132376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"其實升中分返兩條隊已經改善到個情況<br />\n咁樣對女仔都係好事黎<br />\n好多靠背書升到band 1既女仔根本跟唔到band 1學校既課程<br />\n佢又辛苦 老師又辛苦 本身分隊前升到band 1既男仔又受害<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116f0a1ce3037e00dc0ac0ccda07ba46bbee43ac","tid":2325864,"uid":161174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f32935ea23b55e5dddc3ff05fd5f39a43e876c7","tid":2325864,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"on9 怪就怪班仔廢囉 唔讀書走去話制度對仔唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9d93cd3fd6d5fb20b8203d2783fcedf5708294","tid":2325864,"uid":387165,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d15b226801e78b75d2b26296dafa493ea91738e","tid":2325864,"uid":387165,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd82aa780e41b4df2abdccec900de105ae8ee503","tid":2325864,"uid":79117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59f75b6355b6cf3197f33541050397a0ce2b7937","tid":2325864,"uid":161174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:02:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99526eb257c77c502e150bc5071220b0809edb37","tid":2325864,"uid":79117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:04: